Yahoo Appoints Munshi CTO While Stata Assumes Entrepreneur Role

-- B y   D a n i e l l e   K u c e r a
-- 
2011-10-17T23:56:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/yahoo-appoints-munshi-cto-while-stata-assumes-entrepreneur-role.html
Yahoo! Inc., the  Internet company 
that’s exploring strategic options after ousting Chief Executive
Officer Carol Bartz, appointed Ash Munshi chief technology
officer, replacing Raymie Stata.  Munshi “has a well-established career managing successful
global technology organizations at the most senior levels with a
laser focus on meeting and exceeding customer needs,”
Sunnyvale, California-based Yahoo said in a statement. Stata is
taking on a newly created role of entrepreneur in residence.  The job changes were previously reported by the
AllThingsDigital technology blog.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Kucera in  San Francisco  at 
 dkucera6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
